=head1 DESCRIPTION

A paginated call to retrieve a list of summary reports of actual Amazon
Web Services charges and the calculated Amazon Web Services charges,
broken down by attributes.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 Arn => Str

The Amazon Resource Number (ARN) that uniquely identifies the billing
group.


=head2 Attributes => ArrayRef[L<Paws::Billingconductor::Attribute>]

The list of key-value pairs that represent the attributes by which the
C<BillingGroupCostReportResults> are grouped. For example, if you want
the Amazon S3 service-level breakdown of a billing group for November
2023, the attributes list will contain a key-value pair of
C<"PRODUCT_NAME"> and C<"S3"> and a key-value pair of
C<"BILLING_PERIOD"> and C<"Nov 2023">.


=head2 AWSCost => Str

The actual Amazon Web Services charges for the billing group.


=head2 Currency => Str

The displayed currency.


=head2 Margin => Str

The billing group margin.


=head2 MarginPercentage => Str

The percentage of the billing group margin.


=head2 ProformaCost => Str

The hypothetical Amazon Web Services charges based on the associated
pricing plan of a billing group.



